and distributed for the Microsoft Windows platform (Windows 10 and later).
Support for Linux-based operating systems and macOS is planned for a future
release and will be announced on the official website at nocorps.org.
NoCorps.org build by KANAGARAJ-M makes no warranty or guarantee regarding the timeline for
additional platform support. Installation and usage of the Software on
unsupported platforms is at the user's own risk and is not covered by any
support obligations from the Author.

